      "description": "2020 sedan in fair condition. The exterior has noticeable scratches and minor dents from regular use. Mechanically functional, but has some issues that may need attention in the near term. The interior shows moderate wear including worn upholstery and some scuffs on trim surfaces. Suitable for a buyer comfortable with a used vehicle that will likely require some maintenance.",
